quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  44,30,We saved the Children of Israel from their humiliating torment
  44,31,"at the hands of Pharaoh: he was a tyrant who exceeded all bounds"
  44,32,We knowingly chose them above all other people
  44,33,and showed them signs in which there was a clear test
  44,34,Yet those who deny the truth say
  44,35,there is nothing beyond our first death; we shall not be raised again
  44,36,"So bring our fathers [back], if what you say is true"
  44,37,"Are they better than the people of Tubba' and those who came before them? We destroyed them, because they were guilty of sin"
  44,38,We did not idly create the heavens and the earth and all that lies between them
  44,39,"We did not create them save with a purpose, yet most people have no knowledge of this"
  44,40,"Truly, the Day of Decision is the appointed time for all of them"
  44,41,"the Day when no friend shall be of the least avail to another, nor shall any be helped"
  44,42,"save those to whom God shows mercy. Surely, He is the Mighty, the Merciful One"